{"tid":1584433,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普撤除逾400種中國貨品關稅","createTime":"2019-09-21T06:08:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-21T13:24:35.000Z","uid":252013,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"61d54897f43a498dac08bdf427146825e2082911","tid":1584433,"uid":252013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T06:08:12.000Z","msg":"好消息點解美股跌？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n00:46 【特朗普撤除逾400種中國貨品關稅】中美經貿代表團周五在華盛頓舉行第二日會議。美國總統特朗普表示，與中國的貿易談判「取得很多進展」(making a lot of progress)，華府同時宣布撤除對中國加徵的超過400種貨品關稅。<br />\n<br />\n來自秒聞 ‧ 實時財經急報app<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mutemute.com/share.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mutemute.com%2Fshare.php&d=ekRw3fL0jih6ME0SbOEd751e7EkIXHZyG33jvsgDPMQ%3D&h=2e5690ec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mutemute.com/share.php</a>"},{"pid":"d3015c83346667ffe1762e4fff4d551b55bd5eb7","tid":1584433,"uid":191926,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T06:10:49.000Z","msg":"可能係同時間威脅<br />\n<br />\n傾唔惦 要加100%關稅"},{"pid":"05d80fe87f0a1e1b493de32517baf0c516e825e8","tid":1584433,"uid":77143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T06:12:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20190921/bkn-20190921010623970-0921_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20190921%2Fbkn-20190921010623970-0921_00842_001.html&d=ekRw3fL0jih6ME0SbOEd751e7EkIXHZyG33jvsgDPMQ%3D&h=36b7ad24\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20190921/bkn-20190921010623970-0921_00842_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n外媒報道，美國總統特朗普表示，他不需要在2020年美國大選之前，與中國達成貿易協議，並指他「不尋求部分協議」，與他上周稱考慮達成中段協議的說法有出入。<br />\n他又說，中國購買美國農產品並不足夠，認為貿易政策對中國造成嚴重影響，但美國經濟很強勁。"},{"pid":"c01316fa778868fbf8ce7429b0c3281134ce9658","tid":1584433,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislik